Ray Park https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Park 0 Raymond "Ray" Park (born 23 August 1974) is a British actor, author and martial artist. He is best known for playing Darth Maul in Star Wars: Episode I – The Phantom Menace and Solo: A Star Wars Story, Toad in X-Men, Snake-Eyes in G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra and G.I. Joe: Retaliation, and Edgar on Heroes. Raymond_"_Ray_"_Park ( born 23_August_1974 ) is a_British_actor_,_author_and_martial_artist .
